  "texts": [
    "The Rationale Generator G processes prompts guided by self-check system prompts:",
    "• Rejection Self-Check S rej for adversarial prompts p ∈ P adv, guiding the model to produce a rejection rationale r rej.",
    "• Compliance Self-Check S comp for benign prompts p ∈ P benign, leading to a compliance rationale r comp.",
    "The final Rationale Dataset is defined as:",
    "where each rationale r = {r (R), r (F) } includes explicit reasoning r (R) before the final response r (F)."
